fonts-lohit-guru (2.91.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Jeremy Bicha ]
  * Team upload.
  * Import Upstream version 2.91.2:
    - Font name changed from Lohit Punjabi to Lohit Gurmukhi.
  * Update debian/watch, Homepage, and Vcs-* fields.
  * Don't try to build WOFF or EOF fonts since they require sfntly
    which isn't in Debian yet.
  * Don't fail the build for failing tests yet.
  * Don't try to install nonexistent docs.
  * Add appstream metadata.
  * Add fix-appstream-metadata.patch.

